flowchart TD
    Start([Cliente invoca servicio]) --> CheckProtocol{Protocolo?}
    
    CheckProtocol -->|REST| ProxyREST[RollbackPurchaseRestPS<br/>/honduras/card/rest/rollbackPurchase/v1<br/>HTTPS + Basic Auth]
    CheckProtocol -->|SOAP| ProxySOAP[RollbackPurchaseSoapPS<br/>/honduras/card/soap/rollbackPurchase/v1<br/>HTTPS + Basic Auth]
    
    ProxyREST --> ValidateSchema[Validar Esquema XML/JSON]
    ProxySOAP --> ValidateSchema
    
    ValidateSchema -->|Válido| Pipeline[RollbackPurchasePP Pipeline]
    ValidateSchema -->|Inválido| ErrorSchema[Error: Schema Validation Failed]
    ErrorSchema --> End([Retornar Error])
    
    Pipeline --> ApplyTemplate[Aplicar HondurasCardTemplate]
    
    ApplyTemplate --> StageAssignment[StageAssigment:<br/>Asignar Variables]
    
    Note1[Variables asignadas:<br/>service = Card/RollbackPurchase<br/>version = v1<br/>key = Ticket<br/>value = data Ticket<br/>method = SOAP<br/>operationTargetSystem = ReversaPagoTarjeta<br/>targetSystem = Vision+]
    StageAssignment -.-> Note1
    
    StageAssignment --> LogRequest[LoggingRegionalRestBS:<br/>SaveLogInFileSystem REQUEST]
    
    LogRequest --> TransformToDB[Transform:<br/>RollbackPurchaseToPagosWS.xqy<br/>Mapeo: Ticket → PV_TICKET]
    
    TransformToDB --> InvokeGetTicket[Invoke DBGetStatusTicketAdapter]
    
    InvokeGetTicket --> DBGetTicket[(Oracle DB: PagosWSTC<br/>Schema: PAGOSWSTC<br/>Package: OSB_K_RECAUDO_BROKER_HN<br/>SP: OSB_CONS_BROKER_RECAUDO_TICKET)]
    
    Note2[IN: PV_TICKET<br/>OUT: 29 campos<br/>- PV_SUCCESSINDICATOR<br/>- PV_MESSAGES<br/>- PV_NUMEROTARJETA<br/>- PN_ORGANIZACION<br/>- PV_MERCHANTNUMBER<br/>- PN_VALOREFECTIVO<br/>- PV_FECHAEXPTC<br/>- PV_SECUENCIAMOVIMIENTO<br/>- etc.]
    DBGetTicket -.-> Note2
    
    DBGetTicket --> CheckTicketExists{PV_SUCCESSINDICATOR<br/>= SUCCESS<br/>AND<br/>PV_MESSAGES = ''}
    
    CheckTicketExists -->|No| ErrorTicketNotFound[Error: Ticket no encontrado<br/>o con errores]
    ErrorTicketNotFound --> MapError1[GetCustomErrorByStackTraceRegionalRestBS]
    MapError1 --> TransformError1[Transform:<br/>ErrorToRollbackPurchase.xqy]
    TransformError1 --> LogError1[LoggingRegionalRestBS:<br/>SaveLogInFileSystem ERROR]
    LogError1 --> End
    
    CheckTicketExists -->|Sí| TransformToVision[Transform:<br/>RollbackPurchaseToOnlinePayment.xqy]
    
    Note3[Mapeo Ticket → Vision+:<br/>POSUserData = ATX<br/>RRN37 = YYDDDHHMMssssss generado<br/>NumberOfInstallments = 00<br/>MCCType = 6010<br/>RequestType = R Reversal<br/>CardNumber = PV_NUMEROTARJETA<br/>OrgId = PN_ORGANIZACION<br/>MerchantNumber = PV_MERCHANTNUMBER<br/>CardExpirationDate = PV_FECHAEXPTC<br/>TotalSalesAmount = PN_VALOREFECTIVO<br/>Track2Length = 0000<br/>Track2Data = 0000<br/>CardValidationValue = 000]
    TransformToVision -.-> Note3
    
    TransformToVision --> GenerateRRN37[Generar RRN37:<br/>YY = último dígito año<br/>DDD = día del año 001-366<br/>HH = hora 00-23<br/>MM = minutos 00-59<br/>ssssss = secuencia movimiento]
    
    GenerateRRN37 --> InvokeVision[Invoke onlineTransactions_v4]
    
    InvokeVision --> VisionPlus[Vision+ OnlineTransactions<br/>http://172.28.1.145:7802/OTWS/v4<br/>Operation: OnlineUpdateCard<br/>Timeout: 70s<br/>Connection Timeout: 65s]
    
    Note4[Request Vision+:<br/>OnlinePaymentV4Request<br/>con RequestType=R]
    VisionPlus -.-> Note4
    
    VisionPlus --> CheckVisionApproved{trim ActionDescription<br/>= APPROVED}
    
    CheckVisionApproved -->|No| ErrorVisionRejected[Error: Reversión rechazada<br/>por Vision+]
    ErrorVisionRejected --> MapError2[GetCustomErrorByStackTraceRegionalRestBS]
    MapError2 --> TransformError2[Transform:<br/>ErrorToRollbackPurchase.xqy<br/>messaggeOnlinePayment = ActionDescription]
    TransformError2 --> LogError2[LoggingRegionalRestBS:<br/>SaveLogInFileSystem ERROR]
    LogError2 --> End
    
    CheckVisionApproved -->|Sí| TransformToActTicket[Transform:<br/>RollbackPurchaseToActTicket.xqy<br/>Mapeo: Ticket → PV_TICKET<br/>statusTicket = R → PV_ESTADO_TICKET]
    
    TransformToActTicket --> InvokeActTicket[Invoke DBActTicketAdapter]
    
    InvokeActTicket --> DBActTicket[(Oracle DB: PagosWSTC<br/>Schema: PAGOSWSTC<br/>Package: OSB_K_RECAUDO_BROKER_HN<br/>SP: OSB_ACT_BROKER_RECAUDO_TICKET)]
    
    Note5[IN:<br/>- PV_TICKET<br/>- PV_ESTADO_TICKET = R<br/>OUT:<br/>- PV_SUCCESSINDICATOR<br/>- PV_MESSAGES]
    DBActTicket -.-> Note5
    
    DBActTicket --> CheckUpdateSuccess{PV_SUCCESSINDICATOR<br/>= SUCCESS}
    
    CheckUpdateSuccess -->|No| ErrorUpdateFailed[Error: Actualización<br/>de ticket fallida]
    ErrorUpdateFailed --> MapError3[GetCustomErrorByStackTraceRegionalRestBS]
    MapError3 --> TransformError3[Transform:<br/>ErrorToRollbackPurchase.xqy]
    TransformError3 --> LogError3[LoggingRegionalRestBS:<br/>SaveLogInFileSystem ERROR]
    LogError3 --> End
    
    CheckUpdateSuccess -->|Sí| TransformSuccess[Transform:<br/>PagosWSToRollbackPurchase.xqy]
    
    Note6[Construir response exitoso:<br/>StatusInfo/Status = SUCCESS<br/>StatusInfo/ValueDate = current-date<br/>StatusInfo/DateTime = current-dateTime<br/>StatusInfo/GlobalId = del request]
    TransformSuccess -.-> Note6
    
    TransformSuccess --> LogResponse[LoggingRegionalRestBS:<br/>SaveLogInFileSystem RESPONSE]
    
    LogResponse --> ReturnSuccess[Retornar Response Exitoso]
    
    ReturnSuccess --> End
    
    style Start fill:#90EE90
    style End fill:#FFB6C1
    style ProxyREST fill:#87CEEB
    style ProxySOAP fill:#87CEEB
    style Pipeline fill:#DDA0DD
    style DBGetTicket fill:#FFD700
    style VisionPlus fill:#FFA500
    style DBActTicket fill:#FFD700
    style ErrorSchema fill:#FF6B6B
    style ErrorTicketNotFound fill:#FF6B6B
    style ErrorVisionRejected fill:#FF6B6B
    style ErrorUpdateFailed fill:#FF6B6B
    style ReturnSuccess fill:#90EE90
    style CheckProtocol fill:#F0E68C
    style CheckTicketExists fill:#F0E68C
    style CheckVisionApproved fill:#F0E68C
    style CheckUpdateSuccess fill:#F0E68C
    
    classDef noteStyle fill:#FFFACD,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    class Note1,Note2,Note3,Note4,Note5,Note6 noteStyle
